org.jhove2.module.display
Interface Displayer

All Superinterfaces:
Module, Reportable
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractDisplayer, JSONDisplayer, TextDisplayer, XMLDisplayer, XSLDisplayer
public interface Displayer
extends Module

Interface for displayer modules, which are responsible for formatting application output.

mstrong, slabrams, smorrissey
